# Transient git worktrees from background agents — never commit
.claude/worktrees/

# Skills ARE committed for cross-session persistence (the remote container is
# reclaimed on inactivity; committing them means a fresh clone has them with no
# `npx skills add` reinstall):
#   .agents/skills/   = real skill content (installed via the skills CLI)
#   .claude/skills/*  = symlinks into .agents/skills (Claude Code's discovery path)
#   skills-lock.json  = the manifest (already tracked)
